{"tid":254711,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"會員呀呀呀呀呀呀呀你隻食屎狗入一入","createTime":"2017-05-23T11:36:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-23T23:46:00.000Z","uid":74981,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b7c27870fc70eb6f12882f739de7fc1007e74266","tid":254711,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T11:36:44.000Z","msg":"真係入黎俾我撚咁on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好啦，就如你所願<br />\n<br />\n1. 大言不慚，話我唔識食<br />\n<img src=\"https://s4.postimg.org/xc3jfea31/Screenshot_2017-05-23-19-04-54.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs4.postimg.org%2Fxc3jfea31%2FScreenshot_2017-05-23-19-04-54.png&h=f26049de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 就睇下你有幾識食，哦，原來呀媽係女人，快餐店工場野，落味精同翻叮到俾你發現到，你好叻叻豬呀<br />\n<img src=\"https://s21.postimg.org/yckmhabiv/Screenshot_2017-05-23-19-07-23.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs21.postimg.org%2Fyckmhabiv%2FScreenshot_2017-05-23-19-07-23.png&h=c798a4aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 咁你咁撐茶記，咁撚識食，唔通你認為茶記冇味精? 可能狗既味覺同人類唔通<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://s7.postimg.org/oip6ftj1n/Screenshot_2017-05-23-19-08-57.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs7.postimg.org%2Foip6ftj1n%2FScreenshot_2017-05-23-19-08-57.png&h=33c2834b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. 教精你啦，唔係樣樣野即整，有獲氣就點好食架，茶記亦有翻叮既野，唔好睇唔到就當冇啦on9。茶記d豬扒，炸雞脾好多都好撚難食。不過你食開狗餅，我用人類既角度同你講食你實唔認同架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n繼續食番你d狗餅啦，我唔再彈佢地啦，食得開心d<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1fcaee29272d61808aa51dbaeba97d5a4e66bd8","tid":254711,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T11:53:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a92a781c0fa0fc7f021ac2e7110d1c8b153a5b58","tid":254711,"uid":40509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":